OUR VISION

Creativity Creates Change

WHY?

It is possible, we want to show that. ELEMINTZ wants to help progress the world with a sustainable ecosystem while we grow exponentially into the future as a community. “The further we as a community grow into the future and create and revolutionize technology, our world must stay sustainable to enjoy our creativity blossom” - Robert Shirak Jr.

WHAT?

Our collection of 13,000 NFTs are authentically hand drawn by our co-owner and in-house artist, Vincent Santana. The originality of our project will propel us to become a DAO that let’s creativity and positive change continuously generate a 50/50 profit split with our chosen charities. Also in turn generating long term passive income for our holders.

HOW?

With the support of our community members after our first collection drop the hard work starts again, the second project begins! THE NEW FACE OF ELEMINTZ. THE DAO. New team members, new community idea implementation, and a new NFT marketplace are all on the horizon for the future of ELEMINTZ. Get involved and the next big idea might have your name on it.

ROADMAP

  • September 27th 2021

    The Genesis

    When it all started… ELEMINTZ came together to create a blueprint of an NFT collection that can generate money nonstop for charities, sustainable passive income to its holders and valuable ELEMINTZ utilities. We wanted to ensure that our collection makes a mark not only with our community members but also the world by donating to global charities to create a sense of world wide unity with ELEMINTZ.

  • November - December

    Commitment

    ELEMINTZ was initially created with the intention of debuting a collection with a relatable message that can inspire collectors to engage while simultaneously generating continuous income for different charities. Two cousins decided to rid themselves from social norms and constructs by creating not only opportunities for themselves but for the community who believe in their mission. With years of a family bond, artistic and technological backgrounds, these cousins meshed their skills together and took advantage of a new world platform to display their talents, intentions, and initiatives. Their first creation is planned to be dropped on the Solana blockchain on March 1st 2022.

  • January 2022

    The Work

    Starting with the heart of ELEMINTZ, the art encapsulates the significance of the world around us to drive the integration of unity with a refreshing, relevant flare. The first collection features four elements: Air Fire Water Earth & some surprises. In order to start the growing ELEMINTZ community, the implementation of Discord plays a huge role for the ELEMINTZ team to directly communicate with their holders in order to provide insight on launch dates, whitelist information, team updates, charity chats, giveaways etc.

  • February 2022

    Reality is Creativty Finished

    Complete finalization of the project ELEMINTZ. Generously generationing 13,000 unique element based NFT’s. THE ROLL OUT BEGINS! Website officially dropped. Discord officially dropped. Twitter officially dropped. Instagram officially dropped. Organic marketing comences NOW.

  • March 2022

    Launch Month

    OFFICIAL DROP MARCH 1ST 2022 4 PM EST. Upon 100% sellout, millions of dollars will be generated for our 4 world-wide charities: One Tree Planted, Generosity.org, The Rainforest Trust, and Clean Air Task Force. On top of our community helping the world, Elemintz intends to award their top 100 community members who push our mission with the utmost passion with 1.9 million dollars in rewards.

  • Post Launch

    What Now?

    First let’s celebrate. Now it’s back to work. All ELEMINTZ holders will be eligible for rewards, raffles, contests and giveaways. Our holders not only own our NFTs but are the only ones eligible to partake in our exclusive future expansions. Along with the exclusivity is the chance to also propose expansion ideas to the ELEMINTZ team for potential future implementation. Future areas for expansion with ELEMINTZ include but not limited to: Staking, The Metaverse, Token Integration, iOS, Android, PC & Mac Gaming. WE are a community and by uniting with ELEMINTZ your voice is heard and your creativity treasured. NOW IT’S TIME TO HAVE FUN.
